{"tid":1291223,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[從賠率內找不同] 一齊發下夢，估下下一場開咩啦","createTime":"2019-07-06T19:05:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T02:51:48.000Z","uid":219681,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"23272535c25f3ab7a6e3d71ebb614aeb1c9fb5eb","tid":1291223,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T19:05:31.000Z","msg":"呢場馬好熱，巴打們有冇心水<br />\n每注金額 : 催淚彈罐一粒<br />\n預計派彩 : 如一注獨贏，香港人將失去自由<br />\n<br />\n第一班<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">香港地，777米，福地</span><br />\n<br />\n1) <span style=\"color: red;\">棄車保帥</span> 獨贏 3.6<br />\n    分析︰風起了，壯士斷臂，送頭搶民心，高官下台從商，效力與「暫緩」相近<br />\n<br />\n2) <span style=\"color: red;\">暪天過海</span> 獨贏 1.6<br />\n    分析︰假扮善意，拉攏敵人，製造時代，政念，立場矛盾，分化，模糊行動焦點<br />\n<br />\n3) <span style=\"color: red;\">借刀殺人</span> 獨贏 <span style=\"color: red;\">1.3</span><br />\n    分析︰勇武 VS 鄉黑 。 速龍 VS 勇士 。 國安 VS 和理非 。劉馬車 VS 短裙港女。監警會 VS 獨立調查委員會。<br />\n<br />\n4) <span style=\"color: red;\">欲擒故縱</span> 獨贏 1.8<br />\n    分析︰表面求和，實質偷襲，攻其不備，高調搜補，低調釋放，再偷偷控告。控制主流媒體消息發放，製造白色恐怖<br />\n<br />\n5) <span style=\"color: red;\">破斧沉舟</span> 獨贏 41<br />\n    分析︰取消通識，強推國教，再啟廿三條，加大發展東大嶼，引入警方投考解放軍制度，單程証提升至每日1500，控告記者，拘捕維權律師，強迫醫教界表忠<br />\n<br />\n6) <span style=\"color: red;\">偷梁換柱</span> 獨贏 12.5<br />\n    分析︰放棄與各大學生會討論，引入愛國青年議政，自製大台，聯合大學校董會認受，利用愛國愛黨喉舌營造時代大和諧假象<br />\n<br />\n7) <span style=\"color: red;\">借屍還魂</span> 獨贏 25.5<br />\n    分析︰利用忽然反共之網絡紅人宣揚階段勝利，攻擊同路人，割席勇武派，打擊隊友士氣，同時控制風向，推廣無前設談判，假以大和解，製造昇平假象，從而騎劫訴求<br />\n<br />\n8) <span style=\"color: red;\">隔岸觀火</span> 獨贏 27<br />\n    分析︰瘋狂批出不反對通知書，請君入甕，大開中門，迫令敵人盡顯窮兇極惡之一面，再予以批判，趁火打劫，待其自取滅亡<br />\n<br />\n9) <span style=\"color: red;\">以逸待勞</span> 獨贏 55<br />\n    分析︰假之以便，唆其使前，再冷漠回應，於精神上將對方陷之死地，令敵人因氣餒而自動送頭，士氣大降<br />\n<br />\n10) <span style=\"color: red;\">走為上策</span> 獨贏 1000<br />\n    分析︰林鄭下台？唔好發夢啦<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">心思細密既香港人，有冇心水？<br />\n我已經冇得再輸，再輸老婆仔女都走佬啦<br />\n我愛香港，我唔想走</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"728a026610148155d20cf02aa1702b8e06c94740","tid":1291223,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T19:06:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd50ca7b9f919ac9a2855bdc12bd65afb2472bf7","tid":1291223,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T19:06:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食粥食飯就睇呢鋪啦"},{"pid":"42158d6ba059ea843d847564673793561afde045","tid":1291223,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T19:07:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 十萬心急"},{"pid":"c6ff918aef1266d980923a810eaaa9bc51a78c04","tid":1291223,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T19:08:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bfbd023d14a8ddeacb247c973bd74186f72cdb8","tid":1291223,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T19:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你班友都唔賭錢架"},{"pid":"11ed159a7814013df63a00dc102864a97463aba9","tid":1291223,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T19:09:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec558af80b67d6c03e6f3b0716731ce392577c8","tid":1291223,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T19:09:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edfa482a6af12c2ccc8231c5e1ac1857a9a3e74c","tid":1291223,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T19:10:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98b9be9fdf8d1269359002758f8daa5fd810272","tid":1291223,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T19:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b1bce79cb5040defcd95789dd6bba9ec5fc011","tid":1291223,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T19:12:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe9671f1fa47052218cc512b5fb769c469bcef24","tid":1291223,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T19:12:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d23bf4dc5db1e0743edf61f383de78279cfeb54","tid":1291223,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T19:15:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45cdd34e762663b2ab580ff2251ca50f9084b5c","tid":1291223,"uid":183878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T19:17:35.000Z","msg":"反正成日發夢唔差在今次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就落隻爆冷走為上策啦,玩住一粒催淚彈罐先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3393ee7fc2427d06ab8ca8f02407dcd54b6408fc","tid":1291223,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T19:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"486b0ec6850600069357f0e4f453fb86de80e281","tid":1291223,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T02:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fabad53e683f464b205f34e718803a05b60913a9","tid":1291223,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T02:51:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}